              "type": "register",
              "value": "external",
              "register": "MODE.TRIG_SRC"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "description": "When enabled, pad 2 (TRIG) becomes an external pulse input that the chip uses as a haptic-effect trigger; firmware switches the DRV2605 into external-trigger mode."
